</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="2.[160,1156,332,1710]" lastBlockId="3.[160,1156,1599,1694]" lastPageId="3" lastPageNumber="460" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">
Features shared by species of the 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Friese" authorityYear="1908" box="[643,761,1581,1606]" class="Insecta" family="Megachilidae" genus="Megachile" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="459" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="leucografa">
<emphasis box="[643,761,1581,1606]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="459">leucografa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
